Muscle Properties, Gross Motor Performance, and Quality of Life in Children With 
Sickle Cell Disease.

Rock K(1), Ho S, Gray VL, Addison O, York T, Keegan Wells D, DeLuca H, Marchese 
V.

Author information:
(1)Departments of Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation Science (Drs Rock, Ho, 
Gray, Addison, and Marchese) and Pediatrics (Dr York), University of Maryland 
School of Medicine, Baltimore, Maryland; Department of Hematology/Oncology, 
