Burden of non-communicable diseases and the achievement of the sustainable 
development goals in 2030 in Mercosur countries.

Malta DC(1), Gomes CS(2), Veloso GA(3), Dias de Andrade FM(4), Souza JB(5), 
Freitas PC(6), Vasconcelhos de Oliveira PP(7), Naghavi M(8), Pinho Ribeiro 
